  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Compare the treatment efficacy of black cohosh extract 80 mg daily and placebo for moderate
      to severe menopausal symptoms
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Compare the treatment efficacy of black cohosh extract 80 mg/day an placebo for moderate to
      severe menopausal symptoms with Kupperman menopausal index and MENQOL
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
